To develop affordable real - time, and rich UI application based on React Native Framework.

What Is React Native?

React Native is a JavaScript library that helps to build user-interface,it combines the best parts of native development with React and offers the apps equipped with extraordinary features.

At Sahajanand Infotech, we have a team of expert React Native application developers. They provide our clients with the best-in-class mobile application development service with React Native.

React Native lets you build genuinely native apps therefore you don’t need to compromise with your users’ experience. It allows you to build mobile apps with a native look, and performance.

We believe in transparency that’s why our clients trust us the most.By joining hands with us will give you a professional, responsive, and dedicated team that is concerned about your project

Why Choose Us?

Our team of developers is dedicated to providing stable, secure, scalable, and reliable mobile applications based on React Native.

We are a professional React Native app development company with sprawling titles that ensure all forms of apps are easy to use.

Through cost-effective, high-quality approaches, we help our clients to transform their innovative ideas into smartphone apps.

We aim to offer all the latest technologies to allow faster delivery time and shorter development process with the React Native.

We guarantee to provide the maximum revenue and download for our customers, with our innovative approach and broad market vision.

Why Choose React Native for Mobile App Development

When you are starting your business, money is the most significant factor you are concerned about. Every start-up wants to achieve fast returns to survive in the tech-savvy market. One has to develop faster and stay longer.

It allows you to use the same code for developing both Android and IOS applications. Thus, it gives the same performance outcome without any additional changes. Within no time you can design a mobile application for your kind of business. The need for different languages like JAVA, Swift, C++ or any other is no longer required. All you need is a JavaScript developer that is profound with native UI library, APIs, and hybrid mobile app development.

  • Expertise in developing simple and complex apps within the best turnaround times
  • Flutter apps are developed with tailored designs to match and enhance the brand value.
  • We develop exceptional applications infused with excellence in performance.
  • Our designs and development frameworks are unique hence delivering out-of-box solutions.
  • We develop secure and scalable ios applications to maintain integrity.
  • Platform channel data type support and codecs

React Native App Development Process

Understanding The Project

We gather requirements, discuss the idea, brainstorm upon it and clarify all doubts regarding the project in advance.

Wireframing And Planning

Wireframing, prototyping, and feasibility analysis is done before proceeding to the design or development phase.

Graphic And UI Designing

Visual components & plans, like design strategy, psds and screens are crafted at the next step of the project development process.

Development And Optimization

Our developers create functional elements, algorithms, and other backend modules while integrating them with ui at this step.

Quality And Extension

Required changes are made, quality assurance is performed and security audit is done once the first draft is ready.

First Draft To Final Delivery

The first draft of the project is shown to the client. Once requirement changes are made and approved, we launch the project.
